						<div class="sticky-wrapper sound-360">
							<h3 class="visuallyhidden">360-degree audio</h3>
							<p class="typography-homepod-intro sound-copy copy-container">Jam-packed with innovation, HomePod mini delivers unexpectedly big sound for a speaker of its size. At just 3.3 inches tall, it takes up almost no space but fills the entire room with rich <span class="highlight-copy">360&#8209;degree audio</span> that sounds amazing from every angle.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="sticky-wrapper sound-audio">
							<picture id="overview-sound-components-1" class="overview-sound-components" data-picture-lazy-load data-download-area-keyframe='{"start":"t - 200vh"}'>
