							<div class="copy-container audio" data-component-list="FocusHandler">
								<div class="typography-homepod-intro">
									<h3 class="copy-block-headline highlight-copy">Boundary-pushing computational audio</h3>
									<p class="copy-block-paragraph">creates the full, detailed tones of a much larger speaker — and HomePod mini turns it up without missing your voice commands.</p>
								</div>
								<div class="cta-links typography-homepod-cta">
									<button data-modal-open class="cta" aria-label="Learn about the boundary-pushing audio components in HomePod mini." data-analytics-title="open modal | see how it works" data-analytics-click="prop3:open modal | see how it works" data-analytics-intrapage-link>See how it works</button>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
