							<div class="copy-container fit">
								<h3 class="visuallyhidden">Designed to fit anywhere in the house</h3>
								<p class="typography-homepod-intro">HomePod mini is <span class="highlight-copy">designed to fit anywhere in the house.</span> Its elegant shape is wrapped in a perfectly seamless mesh fabric that’s virtually transparent to the sound passing through it. A backlit touch surface on the top provides quick control.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
