					<div class="large-8 large-centered medium-10 small-12">
						<div class="typography-homepod-intro" data-component-list="ScrollAnimation" data-anim-keyframes='[{"start": "t - 90vh", "end": "t - 70vh", "breakpointMask": "LXM", "y": ["20px", "0px"]}, {"start": "t - 80vh", "end": "t - 70vh", "breakpointMask": "S", "y": ["20px", "0px"]}]'>
							<h3 class="copy-block-headline highlight-copy">HomePod mini works effortlessly with your Apple devices.</h3>
							<p class="copy-block-paragraph">Pick up an incoming call from your iPhone, listen to music on your Mac, or upgrade your TV experience by taking the sound from your Apple TV to the next level — they all connect to HomePod mini.</p>
