			</picture>
		</noscript>
				</div>
				<div class="section-content row" data-component-list="ScrollAnimation" data-anim-keyframes='[{"start": "t - 100vh", "end": "t - 50vh", "breakpointMask": "LXM", "y": ["10px", "0px"]}, {"start": "t - 90vh", "end": "t - 40vh", "breakpointMask": "S", "y": ["10px", "0px"]}]'>
					<div class="column large-6 small-12">
						<h3 class="visuallyhidden">Hand off music and podcasts between HomePod mini and iPhone</h3>
						<p class="typography-homepod-intro">If you’re enjoying music or a podcast and have to head out, you can <span class="highlight-copy">continue to listen on your iPhone</span> without missing a beat. Hand it off simply by bringing your iPhone close to HomePod mini. And coming soon, you’ll experience the feeling of your iPhone and HomePod mini connecting virtually as the sound transfers.<sup class="footnote footnote-number"><a href="#footnote-2" aria-label="Footnote 2">2</a></sup></p>
					</div>
					<div class="column large-6 small-12">
						<h3 class="visuallyhidden">Hand off music and podcasts between HomePod mini and iPhone</h3>
						<p class="typography-homepod-intro">Also coming soon are personalized listening suggestions that will automatically appear on your iPhone when you hold it next to HomePod mini. You’ll have instant control at your fingertips without having to unlock your iPhone.<sup class="footnote footnote-number"><a href="#footnote-3" aria-label="Footnote 3">3</a></sup></p>
					</div>
				</div>
