						<h3 class="copy-block-headline highlight-copy">Intercom also works with your other Apple devices</h3>
						<p class="copy-block-paragraph">so you can send and receive messages through CarPlay while you’re driving, on your AirPods during a workout, or with your Apple Watch when you’re running errands.<sup class="footnote footnote-number"><a href="#footnote-7" aria-label="Footnote 7">7</a></sup></p>
