					<p class="typography-homepod-intro large-8 large-centered medium-9 small-12">Whether you already have a smart home or are buying your first smart device, <span class="highlight-copy">getting set up — and staying connected from anywhere — is a snap</span> with the Home app and HomePod mini.<sup class="footnote footnote-number"><a href="#footnote-5" aria-label="Footnote 5">5</a></sup></p>
