						<div class="typography-homepod-copy-tiles">
							<h3 class="copy-block-headline highlight-copy">HomePod mini only listens for “Hey Siri”</h3>
							<p class="copy-block-paragraph">— so you can speak freely knowing nothing you say is sent out of your home until you activate Siri with a touch, or HomePod mini hears the magic words, “Hey Siri.”</p>
						</div>
					</div>
