			</picture>
		</noscript>
						<h3 class="visuallyhidden">HomeKit secure video support</h3>
						<p class="typography-homepod-copy-tiles">With HomeKit Secure Video support, HomePod mini can analyze the feeds of your supported video cameras, detecting the presence of people and recognizing familiar faces, pets, and cars. All video processing is done right on device before it’s sent end‑to‑end encrypted to iCloud — so <span class="highlight-copy">your recordings can only be seen by you</span> and the people you share them with, not Apple.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
