						<h3 class="visuallyhidden">Siri uses on-device intelligence</h3>
						<p class="typography-homepod-copy-tiles">HomePod mini works with your iPhone for requests like hearing your messages or notes, so they are completed on device <span class="highlight-copy">without revealing that information</span> to Apple.</p>
